General code layout


Needed

- file format to save registration information
- implement any agent to read/write this data

- mail/http/ftp upload interface agent (to support portal)


Pseudo code

if (registration_data_present)
  read_registration_data()
else
  initialize_registration_data()

UI::show_registration_data()
UI::enter_support_question()

if (upload_hardware_config)
  probe_hardware()

if (upload_software_config)
  probe_software()

UI::show_complete_data()

if (online_possible)
  upload_data_online()
else
  save_data_to_floppy()


